>
> ```kotlin
> val stringPlus: (String, String) -> String = String::plus
> val intPlus: Int.(Int) -> Int = Int::plus
> 
> println(stringPlus.invoke("<-", "->"))
> println(stringPlus("Hello, ", "world!")) 
> 
> println(intPlus.invoke(1, 1))
> println(intPlus(1, 2))
> println(2.intPlus(3)) // 类扩展调用
> 
> ```

